trans-unit.source: Represents a table in the data store.
The DesignerDataTable class is one of several types that represent the schema of a data store at design-time.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerDataTable är en av flera typer som representerar schemat för ett datalager i designläge.

trans-unit.source: These schema items are made available to controls by designers implementing the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment> interface.
trans-unit.target: Objekten schemat görs tillgängliga för kontroller av designers som implementerar det <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment>gränssnittet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment>

trans-unit.source: Controls access schema objects by calling the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment.GetConnectionSchema%2A> method of the interface.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerar åtkomst schemaobjekt genom att anropa den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment.GetConnectionSchema%2A>-metoden i gränssnittet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment.GetConnectionSchema%2A>

trans-unit.source: The DesignerDataTable class represents a single table in the data store.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerDataTable representerar en enda tabell i datalagret.

trans-unit.source: A collection of DesignerDataTable objects is returned when you call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDesignerDataSchema.GetSchemaItems%2A> method with the `schemaClass` parameter set to <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataSchemaClass.Tables?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: En samling DesignerDataTable objekt returneras när du anropar den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDesignerDataSchema.GetSchemaItems%2A>metod med den `schemaClass` parametern värdet <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataSchemaClass.Tables?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataSchemaClass.Tables?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDesignerDataSchema.GetSchemaItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable"></xref> class with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable"> </xref> klass med det angivna namnet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable"></xref> class with the specified name and owner.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable"> </xref> klass med det angivna namnet och ägare.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, returns a collection of relationship objects.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en mängd relationen objekt när åsidosätts i en härledd klass.

trans-unit.source: The CreateRelationships method is called the first time the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable.Relationships%2A> property is accessed, to populate the collection of data table relationships.
trans-unit.target: CreateRelationships-metoden anropas för första gången den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable.Relationships%2A>egenskapen används för att fylla mängden data relationerna mellan tabellerna.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataTable.Relationships%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of relationships defined for a table.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling av relationer som definierats för en tabell.

trans-unit.source: A relationship describes a link between two tables in a data store.
trans-unit.target: En relation beskriver en länk mellan två tabeller i ett datalager.

trans-unit.source: The Relationships property returns a collection that represents all the relationships between this table and other tables in the data store.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen relationer returnerar en mängd som representerar alla relationer mellan tabellen och andra tabeller i datalagret.
